problem:
The point $O$ is the center of the circle circumscribed about $\triangle ABC$, with $\angle BOC = 120^{\circ}$ and $\angle AOB =
140^{\circ}$, as shown. What is the degree measure of $\angle
ABC$?

[asy]
pair A,B,C;
draw(Circle((0,0),20),linewidth(0.7));
label("$O$",(0,0),S);
A=(-16,-12);
C=(16,-12);
B=(3,19.7);
